			On the 29th. we all gathered for a bite to eat and a pint or two at Jensens Bøfhus in Copenhagen. <br><br>18 I believe we were, when Durgin and Calgar finally arrived (probably couldn't get a port) and after introducing ourselves to eachother, we soon started chatting like old friends.<br><br>And guess what we all talked about? Yup, you got it, EverQuest!<br><br>We will have a full update for you later on with pic's to boost, so stay tuned!<br><br>- Errol
