            A formal apology from Divine Intervention&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class="NewsUser">Errol 
            - 01-12-2000 at 16:16:16</span> 
            <br>
		  <span class="NewsTitleDescription">After posting on their messageboards, we have recieved an apology...</span>
		  </td>
          <td width="16" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">&nbsp;</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
        <tr bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
          <td width="32" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">&nbsp;</td>
          <td class="NewsText" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
            <br>
			Arakine of Divine Intervention apologized for plagiarizing our website.<br><br>I urge you all to cease any discourteous posting, if that was your intent.<br><br>Lets keep the flaming on the Official EQ Boards ;-)<br><br>/jk<br><br>Admittedly I was personally outraged at the blatant copying of our site, which represents an enourmous investment by both Clarf, myself and the Council, but matters are well on their way to being settled and we can now focus on whats important:<br><br>Having fun in Norrath.<br><br>Hail Aegis Lux!<br><br>- Errol
          </td>
          <td width="16" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">&nbsp;</td>
