      <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
        <tr bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
          <td width="32" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">&nbsp;</td>
          <td class="NewsText" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
            <br>
			Greetings fellow Aegisians and friends,<br><br>And a special salute to Oreagon Hijacker.. err Hilljacker. Master Errol posted that we should all be proud of our website here, and spread the word throughout Norrath. Apparently somebody misunderstood that:<br><br><a href="http://www.geocities.com/divinedrinal/"" target="_blank">Divine Intervention</a><br><br>Well what can we say other than, we are not the only ones that think Master Clarf is doing one helluva job here. This must be considered a major approval of his work. That being said I think they should have posted their referring to our page somewhere a little more obvious than in their picture links.. I mean I had to look at the properties before I could see it came from us... Hmm<br><br>Please feel free to post on their forum.. ;o)
          </td>
